      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable parts car? This vehicle has certainly seen some adventures and shows significant wear and tear, but it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and give it some TLC! It's priced to sell and ready for its next chapter with a new owner who appreciates a diamond in the rough.",
