    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be an ideal choice for someone looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor dents, and clear coat fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to bring it back to peak performance. It\u2019s an honest car that reflects its mileage and years on the road.",
      "price": 21500.0,
